description: Options for downloading fonts to the printer.

properties.description: Downloads only references to fonts. Note: Use when fonts reside in the printer.
properties.name: NONE

properties.description: Downloads all fonts once per page.
properties.name: COMPLETE

properties.description: Downloads only the characters (glyphs) used in the document. Glyphs are downloaded once per page.
properties.name: SUBSET

properties.description: Downloads only the characters (glyphs) used in the document. Glyphs are downloaded once per page. Note: Use when the number of glyphs exceeds 350.
properties.name: SUBSET_LARGE

name: FontDownloading
